title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - MiG 15
description:
The MiG 15 is a Russian fighter jet developed by the Russian company MiG. One of the community members has started to build this aircraft for MSFS 2020. In this video we will have a look at version 1.0 of this aircraft. 

If you want to try the aircraft yourself please download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/11158/mig-15
